name: INVENTORY VOLUME 4 ISSUE 8 Mark Borthwick Cover
description: Our cover stories for Spring-Summer '13 focus on Nepenthes president  Keizo Shimizu and iconic photographer Mark Borthwick. The issue also  features contributions by Craig Stecyk, Marcus Oakley and Scott A.  Sant'Angelo as well as Cone Mills, The Soloist, Leslie Hewitt, Gottlund  Verlag, Takashi Kumagai, Raif Adelberg, and photo essays by James  Pearson-Howes and Osma Harvilahti.
